 Wizkid and Wande Coal Ayo Balogun, the renowned Nigerian singer, popularly as Wizkid has professed his love for Lagos State after an all-night clubbing with his fellow celebrities. The Grammy award winner posted videos from his outing on his Snapchat story from Friday night till the early hours of Saturday. In one of the videos he posted, the self-acclaimed StarBoy wrote, “I love Lagos.” Wizkid visited the club with fellow celebrity singers like Bella Shmurda, Wande Coal, and Buju. Some of the videos also showed Nollywood actress, Osas Ighodaro, as an attendee at the Quilox luxurious nightclub in the Victoria Island area of the state. One of the activities done at the club included crap game played by rolling dice, as seen in Wizkid videos.